<example>

<title>
Pass arguments onto the target page
</title>

<para>
Add the following link to an Interchange page:

<programlisting><![CDATA[
Visit the <a href="[area href='test' arg='arg1=value1/arg2=value2']">test</a> page.
]]></programlisting>

The relevant part of your <filename>test.html</filename> page could then
look like this:

<programlisting>
<xi:include parse='text' href='../files/area/test.html'/>
</programlisting>

</example>
